earthly /ˈɜːθlɪ/

1. ADJ Earthly means happening in the material world of our life on earth and not in any spiritual life or life after death. 尘世的 [ADJ n] 

例： ...the need to confront evil during the earthly life. …尘世生活中对抗罪恶的需要。 

2. ADJ Earthly is used for emphasis in phrases such as no earthly reason . If you say that there is no earthly reason why something should happen, you are emphasizing that there is no reason at all why it should happen. 根本 [ADJ n] [强调] 

例： There is no earthly reason why they should ever change. 他们毫无理由改变。

